hardwareAbstraction
Class NXTRemoteCommand

java.lang.Object
  hardwareAbstraction.NXTRemoteCommand

public class NXTRemoteCommand
extends java.lang.Object

Handles RS485 communication on the master brick. It will send commands over the output stream and read int, bool, float over the input stream. Code Sourced from Lejos Forums (http://www.lejos.org/forum/viewtopic.php?f=7&t=2620)

Author:
cs07cc4

send

public void send(int id,

                 int param1,
                 boolean immediateReturn)
Sends a command with 1 parameter and requests immediateReturn (if true) over RS485.

Parameters:
id - id of the object to be acted on (1,2,3,4) -> (Motor.A, Motor.B, Motor.C, RemoteultrasonicPoller)
command - command id as according to RemoteCommands interface
param1 - parameter to be sent over RS485 (e.g. 200 for motor.setSpeed(200))
immediateReturn - whether to return immediately or not
